"{\"uid\": \"cityam.com-paris-2024-olympics-at-risk-of-empty-seats-amid-ticket-sale-fears\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Featured  Submit a story  Tell us your story.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 45, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Featured  Submit a story  Tell us your story.\", \"from\": 47, \"to\": 92, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Featured  Submit a story  Tell us your story.\", \"from\": 94, \"to\": 139, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"By:Matt Hardy  Deputy Sports Editor - City AM  With just 200 days to go until what has been promised to be one of the most exceptional Olympic Games of the modern age,City A.M.research shows that 55 medal sessions still have tickets available to purchase.\", \"from\": 141, \"to\": 396, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It raises questions over whether ticket prices are too high, whether the demand is there and whether Paris2024has an aura of desirability.\", \"from\": 398, \"to\": 536, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Games get underway on 26 July with an opening ceremony on the River Seine.\", \"from\": 537, \"to\": 615, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 603, \"end\": 614, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"River Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Among the tickets available for purchase are the men's and women's 100m athletics finals and the men's and women's 200m finals at the Stade de France.\", \"from\": 617, \"to\": 767, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 751, \"end\": 766, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Athletics is often seen as the premier event at an Olympiad but with just 200 days to go there remain empty seats.\", \"from\": 769, \"to\": 883, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Among the other sports with medal event tickets available are rugby sevens, handball - which is extremely popular in France - basketball, boxing and swimming.\", \"from\": 885, \"to\": 1043, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1002, \"end\": 1008, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9637979118084186, \"rank\": 0.03725930056378977, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Stay in the game with The Turnover: your weekly roundup of sport business news, expert analysis and behind\\u2011the\\u2011scenes stories from City\\u202fAM's sports desk.\", \"from\": 1045, \"to\": 1198, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Athletics tickets have been priced at \\u20ac990 (\\u00a3775) for premium \\\"Category First\\\" seats for evening sessions, and \\u20ac690, \\u20ac385, \\u20ac195 and \\u20ac85 for Category A-D tickets.\", \"from\": 1200, \"to\": 1361, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have made the point that these prices are lumpy,\\\" World Athletics chief Lord SebastianCoesaid of the Paris 2024 pricing structure last month.\", \"from\": 1363, \"to\": 1508, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1468, \"end\": 1478, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1701607431146819e-18, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In Budapest [2023 World Athletic Championship], we had very affordable tickets.\", \"from\": 1510, \"to\": 1590, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1514, \"end\": 1522, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"score\": 0.9999999953020051, \"rank\": 4.691255095440346e-09, \"text\": \"Budapest\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There are always going to be premium tickets but it is important that our stadiums are full of people that love our sport, not people that can afford to get to an Olympics.\", \"from\": 1591, \"to\": 1763, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Our sport cannot afford to look marginal in big championships.\", \"from\": 1765, \"to\": 1828, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It really is unacceptable.\", \"from\": 1829, \"to\": 1855, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And I do not want people to think that Budapest was a one-off.\", \"from\": 1856, \"to\": 1918, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1895, \"end\": 1903, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"score\": 0.9999999953020051, \"rank\": 4.691255095440346e-09, \"text\": \"Budapest\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is not a one-off, it is not an outlier.\", \"from\": 1919, \"to\": 1963, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is the new standard.\", \"from\": 1964, \"to\": 1989, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And full stadia are absolutely a prerequisite.\\\"\", \"from\": 1990, \"to\": 2037, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Global head of strategy at M&C Saatchi Sport & Entertainment Neil Hopkins toldCity A.M.: \\\"One of the main challenges for the Paris 2024 organisers will be the perception that the ticket prices are comparatively expensive.\", \"from\": 2039, \"to\": 2260, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2164, \"end\": 2174, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1701607431146819e-18, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Seb Coe has been very vocal about the topic and a sport that for many defines the Olympics - these concerns should be taken seriously.\", \"from\": 2262, \"to\": 2397, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Elite sport has survived the cost-of-living crisis because post-pandemic, people have been incredibly eager to return to the real-life experience but Paris is not a cheap destination so this may be playing a part, particularly where visitors from outside Europe are concerned.\", \"from\": 2399, \"to\": 2676, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2550, \"end\": 2555, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999868123, \"rank\": 1.3352145298832068e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"A lot also depends on the expectations of fans in France.\", \"from\": 2678, \"to\": 2736, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2729, \"end\": 2735, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9637979118084186, \"rank\": 0.03725930056378977, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The hopes attached to Team GB athletes ahead of London 2012 were unprecedented.\", \"from\": 2737, \"to\": 2816, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2759, \"end\": 2766, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9951217187047786, \"rank\": 0.0049018232173806365, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 2785, \"end\": 2796, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999998713865434, \"rank\": 1.2861337789063223e-07, \"text\": \"London 2012\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So French fans could be asking themselves Can we win a lot of medals?'\", \"from\": 2817, \"to\": 2887, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2820, \"end\": 2826, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.5420692296853166, \"rank\": 0.8010048229358896, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"because they will want to experience the equivalent of our own super Saturday success.\", \"from\": 2888, \"to\": 2974, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"[Market researcher] Nielsen has predicted the French team will move from eighth to fifth in the medal table but TeamGB are forecast to achieve third place.\\\"\", \"from\": 2976, \"to\": 3133, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2997, \"end\": 3004, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nielsen_ratings\", \"score\": 0.9914205332252217, \"rank\": 0.007584089126743686, \"text\": \"Nielsen\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nielsen_ratings\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nielsen_ratings\"}, {\"begin\": 3023, \"end\": 3029, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.5420692296853166, \"rank\": 0.8010048229358896, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympics are facing a number of core issues as chiefs look to move beyond Tokyo 2020, where fans were banned due to the Covid-19 pandemic.\", \"from\": 3135, \"to\": 3277, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3213, \"end\": 3218, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.999999999998181, \"rank\": 1.6671174191910626e-12, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The International Olympic Committee have also faced calls to see the financial impact lessened, with Paris building just one stadium for this year's summer Games.\", \"from\": 3279, \"to\": 3441, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3283, \"end\": 3314, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 3380, \"end\": 3385, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999868123, \"rank\": 1.3352145298832068e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Britain's proximity to the Games is good news for the French as it's very likely British fans will make a late dash over the Channel to back British athletes as they do all over the world in every sport,\\\" Hopkins added.\", \"from\": 3443, \"to\": 3663, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3444, \"end\": 3451, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999911493465014, \"rank\": 8.849993732318212e-06, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 3498, \"end\": 3504, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.5420692296853166, \"rank\": 0.8010048229358896, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 3525, \"end\": 3532, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999970708124393, \"rank\": 2.301957250328283e-06, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 3585, \"end\": 3592, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999970708124393, \"rank\": 2.301957250328283e-06, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Commercially, the enthusiasm for Team GB has not waned over the decade or so since London 2012 with the British Olympic Association having attracted sponsors as diverse as Adidas, Dreams and Old El Paso to support the team in Paris.\", \"from\": 3665, \"to\": 3898, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3699, \"end\": 3706, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9951217187047786, \"rank\": 0.0049018232173806365, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 3749, \"end\": 3760, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999998713865434, \"rank\": 1.2861337789063223e-07, \"text\": \"London 2012\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 3770, \"end\": 3797, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British Olympic Association\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Olympic_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 3857, \"end\": 3868, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Old_El_Paso\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Old El Paso\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Old_El_Paso\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Old_El_Paso\"}, {\"begin\": 3892, \"end\": 3897, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999868123, \"rank\": 1.3352145298832068e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That underlines the abiding appeal of the Olympics to the UK audience, something the French will be seeking to trigger come the summer.\\\"\", \"from\": 3900, \"to\": 4037, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3959, \"end\": 3961, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.7811594649381073, \"rank\": 0.28014834982559955, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 3986, \"end\": 3992, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.5420692296853166, \"rank\": 0.8010048229358896, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Share this article  Subscribe to the City AM newsletter to have our top stories delivered directly to your inbox.\", \"from\": 4039, \"to\": 4152, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow us for breaking news and latest updates\", \"from\": 4154, \"to\": 4200, \"entities\": []}]}"